data.name: ReadCseOrganization
data.value: select ORGANZTN_ID, TYPE_CODE from CKT_CSE_ORGANIZATN with(readuncommitted) where TYPE_CODE = 'J' order by ORGANZTN_ID

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'JD' order by CAS_PER_FTE_AVG desc

data.name: ReadDashboardStagingPriority3
data.value: select REPORT_MONTH, REPORT_LEVEL, REPORT_LEVEL_ID, AS_OF_DT, CAS_UNDER_ORD_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_NUM, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG, CAS_PER_FTE_RNK, CONTRACTOR_NUM from CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 with(xlock) where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = 'XJ' order by CAS_PER_FTE_AVG desc

data.name: ReadOfficeOfficeStaffing
data.value: select * from ( select T1.OFFICE_ID, T1.COG_TYPE_CODE, T1.COG_CODE, T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE, T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE, T1.OFF_OFFICE from CKT_OFFICE T1 with(readuncommitted) where T1.EFFECTIVE_DATE <= @effectiveDate and T1.DISCONTINUE_DATE >= @effectiveDate and exists ( select * from CKT_CSE_ORG_RELATN T3 with(readuncommitted) where T1.COG_TYPE_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_TYPE and T1.COG_CODE = T3.COG_PARENT_CODE and T3.REASON_CODE = 'JC' and @cogChildType = T3.COG_CHILD_TYPE and @cogChildCode = T3.COG_CHILD_CODE ) ) S1 cross apply ( select top(1) YEAR_MONTH, F_T_E, OFF_GENERATED_ID from CKT_OFFC_STAFFING with(readuncommitted) where S1.OFFICE_ID = OFF_GENERATED_ID and YEAR_MONTH = @yearMonth ) S2

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority1
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set CAS_PER_FTE_NUM = @casPerFteNum, CAS_PER_FTE_DEN = @casPerFteDen, CAS_PER_FTE_AVG = @casPerFteAvg where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId

data.name: UpdateDashboardStagingPriority2
data.value: update CKT_DB_STAGE_PRI12 set CAS_PER_FTE_RNK = @casPerFteRnk where REPORT_MONTH = @reportMonth and REPORT_LEVEL = @reportLevel and REPORT_LEVEL_ID = @reportLevelId
